Description: Gently used, had to switch to a bigger bag for our needs. Retails for $349. Kate Spade Adamson Blake Avenue baby/diaper bag is perfect for moms on the go, a baby shower gift, or just looking fashionable while out strolling baby! This is our last Adamson bag! This roomy bag is made of matte water-resistant nylon, black leather trim and silver hardware. Strong, adjustable, and removable shoulder strap. Top magnetic snap closure. The exterior has the ksny 14 karat light goldplated logo plate, two front slip pockets, two expandable side pockets, and a full-length snap back pocket. The interior has a waterproof lining, stroller/carriage straps (or could be used to extend the shoulder strap) and four interior pockets (one zippered with logo on the pocket). Coordinating changing pad has Kate Spade logo on it. This roomy tote measures about 13.5" L x 13" H x 4" D and could fit a 13" laptop. Baby bag comes new with tag and with Kate Spade care card (not shown) as well as "big world, little baby" Kate Spade store tag. Free Shipping!
